Packages required for installation
  yum install gcc.x86_64
  yum install gcc-c++.x86_64
  yum install gperf.x86_64
  yum install byacc.x86_64
  yum install openssl-devel.x86_64

There may be other packages that weren't installed with your installation of Centos7.
The fresh installation provided by my provider didn't include the packages above.  The
installer will stop when it does not have a required package.  You may have  to do some
searching to find the package needed.   
